URISanitizer - Class in cascading.management.annotation
URISanitizer is an implementation of the Sanitizer interface to sanitize URIs of different kinds (file, HTTP, HDFS, JDBC etc.) Depending on the visibility, the Sanitizer will return different values: PUBLIC: Only return the path of the URI PROTECTED: Same as PUBLIC + query parameters PRIVATE: Same as PROTECTED + URI scheme and authority (host/port)
